t in? Most online lenders are direct lenders with digital processes. They offer convenience and technology-driven experiences. Some provide competitive rates."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "What's \"NEXA\" in Your Homebuying Journey?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Wherever you are in the process, understanding how mortgage brokers and lenders work differently empowers you to choose the right path. Here's how this knowledge connects to your next steps:"}}]};
